episodes.title: The City of New York vs. Homer Simpson
episodes.plot: Homer must travel to New York to get his car back, which is illegally parked at World Trade Center Plaza.

episodes.title: The Principal and the Pauper
episodes.plot: At his 20th anniversary celebration as school principal, Principal Skinner is discovered to be an imposter of the real Seymour Skinner.

episodes.title: Lisa's Sax
episodes.plot: Homer recounts the story of Bart's first day of school, which corresponds with the story of how Lisa got her saxophone.

episodes.title: Treehouse of Horror VIII
episodes.plot: Homer battles mutants after Springfield is annihilated by a neutron bomb; Bart has his DNA mixed with a fly; Marge is revealed to be a witch in colonial Springfield.

episodes.title: The Cartridge Family
episodes.plot: After a massive soccer riot, Homer purchases a gun to protect the family.

episodes.title: Bart Star
episodes.plot: A damning report on childhood obesity in Springfield leads to the formation of a pee-wee football team. After belittling Ned Flanders, Homer ends up coaching the team, but his favoring of Bart makes him unpopular.

episodes.title: The Two Mrs. Nahasapeemapetilons
episodes.plot: Apu receives a letter from his mother stating that it's time for him fulfilled his arranged marriage obligation, he pretends Marge is his wife.

episodes.title: Lisa the Skeptic
episodes.plot: Townspeople believe Lisa has unearthed the fossiled remains of a angel.

episodes.title: Realty Bites
episodes.plot: Marge becomes a real-estate agent.

episodes.title: Miracle on Evergreen Terrace
episodes.plot: When Bart accidentally burns down the family's Christmas tree and gifts, he claims that a robber stole everything. As a result, the town gets them a new tree and pitches in to raise funds.

episodes.title: All Singing, All Dancing
episodes.plot: Homer is disappointed when the western he rented turns out to be a musical, so the family reminds him of the musical moments in the show's history.

episodes.title: Bart Carny
episodes.plot: Bart and Homer befriend two carnies and invite them to stay with them, but the carnies soon swindle the Simpsons out of their house.

episodes.title: The Joy of Sect
episodes.plot: An evil cult called the Movementarians brainwashes the citizens of Springfield and it's up to Marge to get them back.

episodes.title: Das Bus
episodes.plot: While the kids become stranded on a desert island, Homer attempts to cash in on the Internet.

episodes.title: The Last Temptation of Krust
episodes.plot: After a disastrous performance, Krusty changes his image and becomes an edgy stand-up.

episodes.title: Dumbbell Indemnity
episodes.plot: Homer and Moe attempt insurance fraud so that Moe can support his new girlfriend. When Homer ends up in jail, Moe has to decide whether or not to come forward.

episodes.title: Lisa the Simpson
episodes.plot: Lisa fears she is losing her intelligence when she learns about the fabled Simpson gene. Meanwhile, Jasper freezes himself in the Kwik-E-Mart freezer.

episodes.title: This Little Wiggy
episodes.plot: Bart is reluctant to hang out with Ralph Wiggum, until he gains access to Chief Wiggum's master key to the city.

episodes.title: Simpson Tide
episodes.plot: Homer causes an international incident after he joins the Naval reserves.

episodes.title: The Trouble with Trillions
episodes.plot: Homer is forced to spy for the IRS after an audit. But when he is asked to retrieve a trillion dollar bill from Mr. Burns, he switches sides and the two flee to Cuba for refuge.

episodes.title: Girly Edition
episodes.plot: Bart and Lisa become locked in competition when they anchor a children's news program; Homer adopts a helper monkey.

episodes.title: Trash of the Titans
episodes.plot: Homer becomes the sanitation commissioner for Springfield. His ineptitude pollutes the town and leads to a drastic solution.

episodes.title: King of the Hill
episodes.plot: After humiliating Bart at a church picnic, Homer resolves to get in shape. Soon, he is contacted by an energy bar company that wants him to climb a mountain as a promotion.

episodes.title: Lost Our Lisa
episodes.plot: Lisa gets lost after she tries to take a bus to a museum.

episodes.title: Natural Born Kissers
episodes.plot: Homer and Marge's attempt to spice up their marriage leads to the couple being chased naked through Springfield.
